Package: herald
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libnotify-bin
Description: Secure desktop notifications from root to user sessions
 Herald delivers notifications from privileged processes (root, systemd
 timers, cron jobs) to the logged-in user's desktop session, using a
 local socket and libnotify.
